\"label\":\"Events\",\"description\":\"Meet up with the global Aptos community\"},\"forum\":{\"label\":\"Discussion Forum\",\"description\":\"Interact with fellow developers on Aptos\"},\"discord\":{\"description\":\"Engage in global and local Aptos discussions\"},\"getStarted\":{\"label\":\"Get Started\"}},\"links\":{\"skipToMainContent\":\"Skip to main content\",\"assistant\":\"Aptos Assistant\",\"currents\":\"Aptos Blog\",\"useCases\":\"Aptos Use Cases\",\"tokenomics\":\"View Aptos Tokenomics\",\"grants\":\"Aptos Grants\",\"developerResources\":\"Developer Resources\",\"brand\":\"Aptos Brand\",\"getStarted\":\"Get Started with Aptos\",\"about\":\"About Aptos Foundation\",\"privacy\":\"Aptos Privacy\",\"terms\":\"Aptos Terms\",\"events\":\"Aptos Events\",\"profile\":\"Profile\",\"whitepaper\":\"Aptos Whitepaper\",\"whitepaperDownload\":\"View Aptos Whitepaper\",\"subscribe\":\"Subscribe for Updates\",\"careers\":\"Aptos Foundation Careers\",\"community\":\"Aptos Community\",\"regionalCommunities\":\"Aptos Regional Communities\",\"glossary\":\"Aptos Glossary\",\"docs\":\"Aptos Docs\",\"docsMovement\":\"Aptos Move Docs\",\"applyForGrants\":\"Apply for Aptos Foundation Grant\",\"explorer\":\"Aptos Explorer\",\"googleCloudAcceleratorProgram\":\"Apply for Google Cloud Accelerator Program\",\"theRegistryApply\":\"Apply for The Registry\",\"theRegistryExplore\":\"Explore The Registry\",\"artistGrantProgram\":\"Apply for Arist Grant Program\",\"names\":\"Aptos Names\",\"governance\":\"Aptos Governance\",\"nodes\":\"Aptos Nodes\",\"submitEcosystemProject\":\"Submit Project\",\"aptosForum\":\"Aptos Discussion Forum\",\"aptosEcosystemJobs\":\"Aptos Ecosystem Jobs\",\"aptosEcosystemProjects\":\"Aptos Ecosystem Projects\",\"aptosDiscord\":\"Aptos on Discord\",\"aptosGithub\":\"Aptos on Github\",\"aptosLinkedin\":\"Aptos on LinkedIn\",\"aptosReddit\":\"Aptos on Reddit\",\"aptosTelegram\":\"Aptos on Telegram\",\"aptosX\":\"Aptos on X (Formerly Twitter)\",\"aptosCollective\":\"Join the Aptos Collective\",\"aptosCollectiveApply\":\"Apply to be an Aptos Collective Member\",\"aptosLfm\":\"Join Aptos LFM\",\"aptosLfmApply\":\"Apply to Aptos LFM\",\"codeCollision\":\"Code Collision\",\"aptosLabs\":\"Aptos Labs\",\"aptosLabsGithub\":\"Aptos Labs on Github\",\"aptosLabsX\":\"Aptos Labs on X (Formerly Twitter)\",\"climate\":\"Aptos Network Sustainability\"},\"modules\":{\"dato\":{\"forms\":{\"client\":{\"communicationConsentRequired\":\"You must agree to get receive other emails from Aptos\",\"consentToProcessRequired\":\"You must agree to the processing of personal data\",\"fieldRequired\":\"Field is required\",\"emailRequired\":\"Email is required\",\"numberInvalid\":\"Number is invalid\",\"urlInvalid\":\"URL is invalid\",\"dateInvalid\":\"Date is invalid\",\"telInvalid\":\"Telephone number is invalid\",\"emailInvalid\":\"Email is invalid\",\"checkboxRequired\":\"It must be checked\"}}}},\"pages\":{\"brand\":{\"metaTitle\":\"Aptos Brand Assets\",\"metaDescription\":\"Explore Aptos' brand assets. Visual elements reflecting our people-focused mission.\",\"tag\":\"Aptos Brand Assets\",\"heroTitle\":\"Visual Core of the Aptos Brand\",\"heroDescription\":\"Find everything you need here for creating content, media coverage, or sharing information about Aptos. Please review our \u003clink\u003eTrademark Guidelines\u003c/link\u003e before using our logos and brand assets.\",\"logoBlackTitle\":\"Aptos Logo - Black\",\"logoWhiteTitle\":\"Aptos Logo - White\",\"logoSectionTitle\":\"Primary Logo\",\"logomarkSectionTitle\":\"Logomark\",\"logomarkBlackTitle\":\"Aptos Logomark - Black\",\"logomarkWhiteTitle\":\"Aptos Logomark - White\"},\"climate\":{\"metaTitle\":\"Aptos Network Sustainability\",\"metaDescription\":\"Driving sustainability forward by creating a greener, more energy-efficient Web3 for all.\",\"pageTag\":\"climate impact\",\"micaTag\":\"MICA\",\"micaHeading\":\"MiCA Indicators\",\"micaDescription\":\"The following data, which fulfills EU Markets in Crypto Assets (MiCA) requirements, are maintained in partnership with the Crypto Carbon Ratings Institute (CCRI). You can find CCRI's methodology here.\",\"micaDomainsHeading\":\"Domain\",\"micaIndicatorsHeading\":\"Sustainability Indicator\",\"micaDomains\":{\"energyConsumption\":\"Energy\",\"ghgEmissions\":\"GHG Emissions\",\"wasteProduction\":\"Waste Production\",\"naturalResources\":\"Natural Resources\"},\"micaIndicators\":{\"1\":{\"title\":\"Energy consumption\",\"description\":\"Total amount of energy used, expressed in kilowatt-hours (kWh) per calendar year, for the validation of transactions and the maintenance of the integrity of the distributed ledger of transactions.\"},\"2\":{\"title\":\"Renewable energy consumption\",\"description\":\"Share of energy used generated from renewable sources, expressed as a percentage of the total amount of energy used per calendar year, for the validation of transactions and the maintenance of the integrity of the distributed ledger of transactions.\"},\"3\":{\"title\":\"Energy intensity\",\"description\":\"Average amount of energy used, in kWh, per validated transaction.\"},\"4\":{\"title\":\"Scope 1 - controlled\",\"description\":\"Scope 1 GHG emissions, expressed in tonnes (t) carbon dioxide equivalent (CO₂e) per calendar year for the validation of transactions and the maintenance of the integrity of the distributed ledger of transactions.\"},\"5\":{\"title\":\"Scope 2 - purchased\",\"description\":\"Scope 2 GHG emissions, expressed in tCO₂e per calendar year for the validation of transactions and the maintenance of the integrity of the distributed ledger of transactions.\"},\"6\":{\"title\":\"GHG intensity\",\"description\":\"Average GHG emissions (scope 1 and scope 2) per validated transaction, expressed in kilogram (kg) CO₂e per transaction (Tx).\"},\"7\":{\"title\":\"Generation of waste electrical and electronic equipment (WEEE)\",\"description\":\"Total amount of WEEE generated for the validation of transactions and the maintenance of the integrity of the distributed ledger of transactions, expressed in tonnes per calendar year.\"},\"8\":{\"title\":\"Non-recycled WEEE ratio\",\"description\":\"Share of the total amount of WEEE generated for the validation of transactions and the maintenance of the integrity of the distributed ledger of transactions, not recycled per calendar year, expressed as a percentage\"},\"9\":{\"title\":\"Generation of hazardous waste\",\"description\":\"Total amount of hazardous waste generated for the validation of transactions and the maintenance of the integrity of the distributed ledger of transactions, expressed in tonnes per calendar year.\"},\"10\":{\"title\":\"Impact of the use of equipment on natural resources\",\"description\":\"Description of the impact on natural resources of the production, the use and the disposal of the devices of the DLT network nodes.\"}},\"carbonRatingsLogoAlt\":\"Carbon Ratings organization logo\",\"micaLastUpdated\":\"Last updated on {updatedAt}\"},\"codeCollision\":{\"metaTitle\":\"Code Collision: Where innovators converge to spark something entirely new\",\"metaDescription\":\"Join Code Collision, a global hackathon for blockchain innovators. Enjoy a flexible virtual and in-person hybrid format and community-hosted Code Jams and Code Stations\",\"hero\":{\"ctaButton\":\"Register Now\"},\"sections\":{\"overview\":\"Overview\",\"prizes\":\"Prizes\",\"resources\":\"Resources\",\"tracks\":\"Tracks \u0026 Prizes\",\"sponsors\":\"Sponsors\",\"judges\":\"Judges \u0026 Mentors\",\"timeline\":\"Timeline\",\"schedule\":\"Additional Events\",\"faq\":\"FAQ\",\"bookEnd\":\"Register\"},\"overview\":{\"tag\":\"Overview\",\"heading\":\"Code Collision: Where innovators converge to spark something entirely new\",\"description\":\"Join Code Collision, a global hackathon for blockchain innovators. Enjoy a flexible virtual and in-person hybrid format along with community-hosted Code Jams and Code Stations. Beginners are welcome—attend our workshops and bootcamps to fine-tune and scale your next big idea.\"},\"prizeAmounts\":{\"tag\":\"Prize Amounts\",\"heading\":\"$$500K Total Prize Pool\",\"description\":\"5 Tracks with 5 Prizes Each\"},\"coreChallenges\":{\"title\":\"Tracks \u0026 Prizes\",\"description\":\"5 Core Challenges\",\"item1Title\":\"DeFi / RWA\",\"item1Description\":\"Lead the charge in decentralized finance and the tokenization of Real World Assets. Design dApps and protocols to create secure, efficient, and transparent financial systems using advanced blockchain technology.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e1st Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$35,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e2nd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$20,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e3rd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$15,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e4th Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$10,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e5th Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$5,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\",\"item2Title\":\"Gaming / NFTs\",\"item2Description\":\"Fuse creativity with technology to craft unique and immersive experiences. Develop blockchain-based games or NFT platforms that enable true ownership and trading of digital assets.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e1st Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$35,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e2nd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$20,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e3rd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$15,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e4th Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$10,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e5th Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$5,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\",\"item3Title\":\"AI / DePIN\",\"item3Description\":\"Leverage the transformative power of AI and blockchain. Develop intelligent applications that harness AI or create decentralized networks that enhance infrastructure efficiency, security, and sustainability. Whether your focus is on AI, DePIN, or both, drive groundbreaking advancements in technology and infrastructure.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e1st Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$35,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e2nd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$20,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e3rd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$15,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e4th Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$10,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e5th Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$5,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\",\"item4Title\":\"Social\",\"item4Description\":\"Reshape social with decentralized platforms that enhance user controls, privacy, creator monetization, and more. Spark innovative solutions that offer new ways to connect and share.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e1st Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$35,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e2nd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$20,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e3rd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$15,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e4th Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$10,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e5th Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$5,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\",\"item5Title\":\"The Unexpected\",\"item5Description\":\"Embrace the element of surprise and push the boundaries of innovation. This category is for projects that don't fit neatly into any other track. Whether you're working on a groundbreaking application, a novel use of technology, or an idea that defies categorization, let your innovations collide in unexpected ways.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e1st Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$35,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e2nd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$20,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e3rd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$15,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e4th Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$10,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e5th Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$5,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\"},\"specialBounties\":{\"title\":\"Special Bounties\",\"description\":\"8 Bonus Challenges\",\"item1Title\":\"UI Challenge\",\"item1Description\":\"Showcase your design skills in the UI Challenge. Open to all developers and designers, no Move coding required. Leverage existing Aptos smart contracts and SDKs to create intuitive and engaging user experiences. Your innovative designs will help bridge the gap between blockchain technology and everyday users, driving mass adoption of decentralized applications.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e1st Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$20,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e2nd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$12,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e3rd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$5,500\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\",\"item2Title\":\"Best Public Goods\",\"item2Description\":\"The Best Public Goods bounty recognizes solutions that benefit the community and ecosystem. Develop projects that enhance accessibility, promote social good, or provide public value using blockchain technology.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e1st Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$20,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e2nd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$12,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e3rd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$5,500\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\",\"item3Title\":\"Aptos Indexer Challenge with NODIT\",\"item3Description\":\"Create an outstanding project using blockchain data with \u003cLinkNoditIndexerAPI\u003eNodit's Indexer API\u003c/LinkNoditIndexerAPI\u003e. Simplify complex data queries and analysis efficiently.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e1st Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$5,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e2nd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$3,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e3rd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$2,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\",\"item4Title\":\"Foresight's Choice: Consumer Applications\",\"item4Description\":\"Build innovative consumer-facing applications that leverage blockchain technology to provide significant value to users. Win bounties for projects that enhance consumer experiences or solve real-world problems.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003eTop Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$5,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\",\"item5Title\":\"Build with Econia\",\"item5Description\":\"Create the best DeFi project using the \u003cLinkEconiaReferenceFrontEnd\u003eEconia reference front end\u003c/LinkEconiaReferenceFrontEnd\u003e on the Aptos blockchain. Leverage Aptos smart contracts and SDKs alongside Econia's pre-built components to develop innovative, user-friendly applications.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003eTop Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$1,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\",\"item6Title\":\"MEXC Venture’s Choice: Best Telegram Integration\",\"item6Description\":\"Leverage the power of the Telegram ecosystem to create innovative projects on Aptos. Integrate community interactions and blockchain technology to build solutions that stand out.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003eTop Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$5,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\",\"item7Title\":\"Kana Labs’ Market Maker Challenge\",\"item7Description\":\"Develop a bot using Kana Labs' perpetual futures contracts (perps) API. Leverage Aptos smart contracts to optimize performance and enhance liquidity. Compete to build the best-performing bot and take home a share of the prize pool.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e1st Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$3,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e2nd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$2,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e3rd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$1,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\",\"item8Title\":\"Mizu Wallet’s Telegram Integration Challenge\",\"item8Description\":\"Build innovative Aptos-based projects that harness the power of the Telegram ecosystem through Mizu Wallet. This challenge encourages creative integrations that enhance user interaction and expand the capabilities of the Aptos network.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e1st Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$3,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e2nd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$2,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cTitle\u003e3rd Prize:\u003c/Title\u003e\u003cDescription\u003e$1,000\u003c/Description\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\"},\"sponsors\":{\"title\":\"Official Sponsors\"},\"judges\":{\"tag\":\"Judges \u0026 Mentors\",\"heading\":\"An exclusive panel of industry experts\"},\"resources\":{\"tag\":\"Resources\",\"heading\":\"Find everything you need to succeed\",\"description\":\"Access beginner guides, advanced tutorials, documentation, and workshops. Whether you're new to Move or expanding your expertise, you'll find the tools and support you need here.\",\"ctaButton\":\"Explore Resources\"},\"eventTimeline\":{\"tag\":\"Event Timeline\",\"heading\":\"Key dates to remember\"},\"eventsSchedule\":{\"tag\":\"Additional Events\",\"heading\":\"More from Code Collision\",\"description\":\"Get the most out of your hackathon journey with a range of optional in-person and virtual events. Join our Code Jams for casual meetups and brainstorming. Want to just build? Stop by a Code Station for heads-down development. You can also participate in online bootcamps and advanced challenges. While these events are not mandatory, they're recommended as a way to meet other builders and explore the Aptos ecosystem.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003eWant to host a Code Jam or Code Station in your city? \u003clink\u003eSubmit a Request\u003c/link\u003e.\"},\"bookEnd\":{\"tag\":\"Register\",\"heading\":\"Are you ready for impact?\",\"description\":\"Connect, code, and collaborate on projects that will resonate across the universe.\",\"ctaButton\":\"Register Now\",\"secondaryButton\":\"View hackathon rules\"},\"faq\":{\"tag\":\"Faq\",\"title\":\"Common questions\",\"item1Title\":\"How does the hackathon work?\",\"item1Content\":\"The hackathon is primarily online, with registration and submissions managed through \u003cLinkDoraHacks\u003eDoraHacks\u003c/LinkDoraHacks\u003e. To support ideation and collaboration, Aptos Foundation and some ecosystem partners are hosting a variety of \u003cLinkEvents\u003eevents globally and online\u003c/LinkEvents\u003e. Attending side events is not required to participate in Code Collision or be eligible for a Prize.\",\"item2Title\":\"What is the difference between Code Jams and Code Stations?\",\"item2Content\":\"Code Jams are casual meetups for developers to collaborate, brainstorm, and innovate through hands-on workshops and networking. In contrast, Code Stations are structured co-working environments that offer focused development time, support sessions, and interactive learning activities. Both types of events provide opportunities to connect with fellow developers and push your projects forward.\",\"item3Title\":\"How can I request to host a Code Jam or Code Station in my city?\",\"item3Content\":\"To request a Code Jam or Code Station in your city, please fill out the \u003cLinkRequestForm\u003erequest form\u003c/LinkRequestForm\u003e available on our website. If your proposal is approved, you will receive a grant to host the event. This support will help you organize and facilitate the gathering, bringing the Code Collision experience to your local developer community.\",\"item4Title\":\"What kind of developer resources will you provide?\",\"item4Content\":\"Participants have access to a \u003cLinkDeveloperGuide\u003ecomprehensive developer guide\u003c/LinkDeveloperGuide\u003e along with the \u003cLinkDeveloperDocs\u003eAptos Developer Docs\u003c/LinkDeveloperDocs\u003e to aid in the development of their hackathon project, whether you’re a new developer, new to Aptos, or a seasoned builder.\",\"item5Title\":\"Can I submit projects for more than one track?\",\"item5Content\":\"Yes, you are welcome to submit a project to a maximum of two tracks. Each submission will be evaluated independently based on its merits. Each submission will also be eligible to win one of the eight special bounties. You may also submit more than one project.\",\"item6Title\":\"Do I need to know Move to participate?\",\"item6Content\":\"No, you don't need to know Move to participate. The UI Challenge is a bounty specifically designed for those who don't have experience with Move. Additionally, there will be various events and resources, including boot camps and workshops, to help new developers onboard and learn Move. These resources are designed to support you throughout the hackathon, regardless of your current skill level with Move.\"}},\"collectibles\":{\"aptos-two\":{\"metaTitle\":\"Aptos Two Mainnet Anniversary NFT\",\"metaDescription\":\"Celebrate two years of Aptos Mainnet with a unique NFT that highlights the ecosystem's growth and progress.\",\"heroTag\":\"Collectibles\",\"heroTitle\":\"Aptos Two Commemorative NFT\",\"heroDescription\":\"Celebrate Two Years of Aptos Mainnet\",\"overview\":{\"content\":\"Celebrate two years of Aptos innovation with a commemorative NFT—marking the ecosystem’s growth, milestones, and the people behind it all.\",\"ended\":\"The minting period for the Aptos Two Anniversary NFT has ended. Thank you to everyone who participated and helped commemorate two years of Aptos' growth and community.\"},\"faq\":{\"how-to\":{\"title\":\"How do I mint the Aptos Two NFT?\",\"content\":\"You need an Aptos-enabled wallet to mint. Connect your wallet, confirm the transaction, and your NFT will be added to your wallet.\"},\"value\":{\"title\":\"Is the Aptos Two NFT free?\",\"content\":\"The Aptos Two NFT is free to mint and intended to be purely commemorative.\"},\"price\":{\"title\":\"Do I have to pay for the transaction?\",\"content\":\"Yes, like with any blockchain transaction, there are associated network gas fees. See the official rules for more details.\"}},\"bookEnd\":{\"secondaryButton\":\"View official rules\"}},\"template\":{\"client\":{\"connectWallet\":{\"description\":\"Establish a connection with your wallet to allow minting NFTs.\"},\"howToMint\":{\"title\":\"How to mint?\",\"connect\":\"Connect Your Wallet\",\"select\":\"Select quantity you want to mint\",\"confirm\":\"Confirm transaction\",\"receive\":\"Receive your NFTs\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"FAQ\"},\"walletProvider\":{\"unknownError\":\"Unknown wallet error\"},\"wrongNetworkDialog\":{\"title\":\"Wrong network\",\"message\":\"Your wallet is currently on “{currentNetwork}”. Please switch to “{targetNetwork}” to continue using the app.\"},\"walletSelector\":{\"copyAddress\":\"Copy address\",\"account\":\"Account\",\"disconnect\":\"Disconnect\",\"copiedAddress\":\"Copied wallet address to clipboard.\",\"failedToCopyAddress\":\"Failed to copy wallet address to clipboard.\"},\"walletConnectDialog\":{\"connectWallet\":\"Connect a wallet\",\"loginOrSignup\":\"Log in or sign up \u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e with Social + Aptos Connect\",\"learnMoreAboutConnect\":\"Learn more about \u003clink\u003eAptos Connect\u003c/link\u003e\",\"or\":\"Or\",\"moreWallets\":\"More wallets\",\"install\":\"Install\",\"connect\":\"Connect\"},\"mint\":{\"copyCollectionToClipboard\":\"Copied collection address to clipboard.\",\"failedCopyCollection\":\"Failed to copy collection address to clipboard.\",\"connectFirst\":\"You must first connect a wallet in order to mint.\",\"insufficientFunds\":\"You do not have enough funds to mint\",\"mintingSuccess\":\"{nftCount, plural, =1 {Token was minted} other {# tokens were minted}} successfully\",\"mintingFailed\":\"Token minting failed...\",\"mint\":\"Mint NFT\",\"mintedCount\":\"{minted} / {maxSupply}\",\"collectionAddress\":\"Collection address\",\"viewOnExplorer\":\"View on Aptos Explorer\",\"tooManyRequests\":\"Too many requests. Please try again later.\"},\"stats\":{\"title\":\"Collection Stats\",\"maxSupply\":\"Created NFTs\",\"totalMinted\":\"Total Minted\",\"uniqueHolders\":\"Unique Holders\"}}}},\"collective\":{\"metaTitle\":\"Join the Aptos Collective\",\"metaDescription\":\"Apply to be an Aptos ambassador and help move the ecosystem forward. Get the opportunity to receive exclusive rewards, support for community events, and access to Web3 leaders \u0026 builders.\",\"tag\":\"Aptos Collective\",\"heroTitle\":\"Join the Aptos Collective: A Global Movement Building the Future of Aptos\",\"heroDescription\":\"The Aptos Collective is an engaged ambassador community uniting enthusiasts from around the world to foster growth and innovation on Aptos. As a member, you’ll gain access to exclusive perks, professional development, and a supportive network of like-minded builders—all while championing a technology you love.\",\"heroCta\":\"Apply to the Collective\",\"inclusivity\":{\"tag\":\"Inclusivity \u0026 Community\",\"title\":\"A Place Where Everyone Belongs\",\"description\":\"From developers and content creators to meetup hosts and community organizers, our Collective brings together diverse talents and backgrounds. Whether you’re brand-new to Aptos or a seasoned pro, you’ll find a home here. We strive to make everyone feel included, heard, and empowered to contribute in ways that match their unique strengths.\"},\"benefits\":{\"tag\":\"Benefits\",\"title\":\"Why join the Aptos Collective?\",\"card1Title\":\"Learning \u0026 Career Development\",\"card1Items1\":\"Access monthly guest speakers, weekly hangout sessions, and exclusive training\",\"card1Items2\":\"Collaborate with Aptos Foundation team members and ecosystem experts.\",\"card2Title\":\"Networking \u0026 Professional Visibility\",\"card2Items1\":\"Showcase your contributions at events, conferences, and on social media.\",\"card2Items2\":\"Expand your professional network with industry leaders and fellow builders.\",\"card3Title\":\"Exclusive Benefits \u0026 Perks\",\"card3Items1\":\"Enjoy early access to new Aptos projects, creator grants, and potential allowlist opportunities across the ecosystem.\",\"card3Items2\":\"Unlock unique roles in Discord/Telegram, plus limited-edition Aptos Collective merch.\",\"card3Items3\":\"Earn a spot in our Vanguard tier—our top ambassador level—featuring monthly awards and added recognition.\",\"card4Title\":\"Support for Your Initiatives\",\"card4Items1\":\"Eligible for community events grants to fund community meetups, workshops, or local events.\",\"card4Items2\":\"Partner with Aptos Foundation on content creation, product testing, and marketing.\"},\"memberDuties\":{\"tag\":\"What Ambassadors Do\",\"title\":\"Amplify Aptos, One Community at a Time\",\"description\":\"Becoming a Collective member comes with a number of benefits—but being a member also allows you to express your passion and contribute to the development of the ecosystem in a meaningful way. You’ll act as a champion of the Aptos ecosystem and network.\",\"card1Title\":\"Create Engaging Content\",\"card1Description\":\"From technical tutorials and social posts to videos and memes—help others learn about Aptos.\",\"card2Title\":\"Localize for Global Reach\",\"card2Description\":\"Translate key materials or discussions to expand Aptos knowledge in your region.\",\"card3Title\":\"Collaborate with Projects\",\"card3Description\":\"Assist ecosystem projects by testing new features, supporting product launches, and gathering community feedback.\",\"card4Title\":\"Host Meetups \u0026 Events\",\"card4Description\":\"Organize local gatherings, workshops, or online sessions to connect Aptos enthusiasts.\"},\"requirements\":{\"tag\":\"Requirements \u0026 Who We’re Seeking\",\"title\":\"Are You a Fit for the Collective?\",\"card1Title\":\"Active Aptos Community Involvement\",\"card1Description\":\"Engage on social channels (X/Twitter, Discord, Forums, Telegram, etc.).\",\"card2Title\":\"Passion for Building\",\"card2Description\":\"Eager to learn, collaborate, and share insights about Aptos, Move, and Web3 at large.\",\"card3Title\":\"Willingness to Contribute\",\"card3Description\":\"Offer your skills and time: host an event, create content, or support global meetups.\",\"card4Title\":\"Team-Player Mindset\",\"card4Description\":\"Work cohesively with other ambassadors and the Aptos Foundation to grow the network.\",\"card5Title\":\"Consistent Engagement\",\"card5Description\":\"Maintain activity over time—quarterly reviews ensure that the most committed members receive additional perks (like Vanguard status).\"},\"apply\":{\"tag\":\"Apply\",\"title\":\"Ready to Make an Impact?\",\"description\":\"We accept new members on a cohort basis, with large onboarding waves held every quarter. Applications are now open for our Summer cohort, and will remain open until Sept. 5, 2025.\",\"description2\":\"Familiarizing yourself with the Aptos community beforehand boosts your chances of success. Show us your enthusiasm, your contributions—or even your creative ideas if you’re just getting started.\",\"ctaButton\":\"Apply Now\"},\"faq\":{\"tag\":\"FAQ\",\"title\":\"Common Questions About the Aptos Collective\",\"item1Title\":\"Are Collective members paid?\",\"item1Content\":\"There’s no standard monthly stipend for all members. However, top-performing contributors may be recognized through our Vanguard tier, which provides a monthly award. Additionally, members have access to grants for events, special incentives, and more.\",\"item2Title\":\"Can I join if I’m new to Aptos?\",\"item2Content\":\"Absolutely! As long as you’re passionate and willing to learn, you’ll find a place in the Collective.\",\"item3Title\":\"I don’t speak English fluently. Can I still join?\",\"item3Content\":\"Yes! We have regional ambassadors worldwide. We encourage multilingual members to localize Aptos content in their communities.\",\"item4Title\":\"How often are new members added?\",\"item4Content\":\"We accept new members on a cohort basis, with large onboarding waves held every quarter. Applications are now open for our Summer cohort, and will remain open until Sept. 5, 2025.\",\"item5Title\":\"What is a Collective Grant?\",\"item5Content\":\"Collective Grants are exclusive to members and can help fund community-building initiatives, such as meetups, educational content, or project testing support.\",\"item6Title\":\"What is the Vanguard tier?\",\"item6Content\":\"Vanguard is our top ~20 ambassadors who consistently demonstrate outstanding contributions. They receive monthly stipends, exclusive mentorship, and additional recognition.\"},\"participants\":{\"tag\":\"Meet the Collective\",\"title\":\"Faces of the Aptos Collective\",\"description\":\"Our community of ambassadors spans every corner of the globe. They’re developers, designers, marketers, content creators, and so much more—united by a shared passion for Aptos.\"}},\"ctrlMove\":{\"metaTitle\":\"Ctrl+Move: A Global Online Hackathon\",\"metaDescription\":\"Join Code Collision, a global hackathon for blockchain innovators. Enjoy a flexible virtual and in-person hybrid format and community-hosted Code Jams and Code Stations\",\"hero\":{\"ctaButton\":\"Register Now\"},\"sections\":{\"overview\":\"Overview\",\"prizes\":\"Prizes\",\"resources\":\"Resources\",\"tracks\":\"Tracks \u0026 Prizes\",\"sponsors\":\"Sponsors\",\"judges\":\"Judges \u0026 Mentors\",\"timeline\":\"Timeline\",\"schedule\":\"Additional Events\",\"faq\":\"FAQ\",\"bookEnd\":\"Register\",\"projectIdeas\":\"Project Ideas\",\"partners\":\"Partners\",\"howToJoin\":\"How to Join\"},\"overview\":{\"tag\":\"Overview\",\"heading\":\"Ctrl+Move: A Global Online Hackathon\",\"description\":\"Aptos wasn’t built to replicate the past. It was built to reimagine what finance could be: composable, lightning-fast, and accessible to anyone, anywhere. With parallel execution, sub-second finality, and low fees at scale, Aptos is infrastructure that works—for developers and for users.\",\"description2\":\"This hackathon is your invitation to build what's missing in DeFi. From liquidity engines to payment rails, from lending protocols to next-gen trading apps—you have the tools. Now it’s time to build something that actually works.\"},\"prizeAmounts\":{\"tag\":\"Prize Amounts\",\"heading\":\"$$100K Total Prize Pool\",\"description\":\"Featuring over $100,000 USD in prizes—including core awards and special bounties from ecosystem partners.\"},\"howToJoin\":{\"title\":\"What to Expect\",\"description\":\"How to Join the Hackathon\",\"item1Title\":\"Register via DoraHacks\",\"item1Description\":\"Sign up on DoraHacks to register for the hackathon.\",\"item2Title\":\"Submit Your Project Idea\",\"item2Description\":\"Share your concept, team details, and what you plan to build.\",\"item3Title\":\"Office Hours \u0026 Workshops\",\"item3Description\":\"Join technical workshops, get feedback, and connect with mentors throughout the build period.\",\"item4Title\":\"Satellite Events\",\"item4Description\":\"Connect with global builders IRL—SF, NYC, Buenos Aires, China, Vietnam, United Kingdom, and Nigeria.\",\"item5Title\":\"Winners Announced\",\"item5Description\":\"Top winning teams will be recognized at Aptos Experience.\"},\"projectIdeas\":{\"tag\":\"Project Prompt\",\"title\":\"Hackathon Project Ideas\",\"description\":\"This is your sandbox for building next-gen DeFi. There are no rigid rules—just one expectation: build something meaningful. Whether you're experimenting with liquidity design, new asset types, or better user flows, we're looking for projects that rethink how finance works in an open, scalable world. Here are a few ideas to get you started.\",\"card1Title\":\"Trading \u0026 Market Infrastructure\",\"card1Description\":\"\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003ePush the limits of CLOBs, matching engines, and advanced order types\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003eBuild vault strategies, analytics dashboards, or custom DeFi tooling\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003eIntegrate with Aptos-native protocols like Merkle Trade, Hyperion, and Tapp\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\",\"card2Title\":\"New Financial Products\",\"card2Description\":\"\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003eCreate RWA markets, prediction games, or options protocols\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003eBuild trading bots, social investing tools, or mobile-first UIs\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003eExperiment with novel vault mechanics or capital coordination strategies\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\",\"card3Title\":\"Payments \u0026 Value Transfer\",\"card3Description\":\"\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003eDesign real-time remittance, payroll, or treasury systems\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003eLaunch stablecoin apps that work across borders and devices\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003eBring off-chain users on-chain with clean fiat on/off ramps\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003eLeverage Circle's CCTP to build crosschain payroll systems, merchant settlement layers, or subscription-based commerce with USDC natively settled on Aptos\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003eUse Circle Wallets for embedding secure, flexible and scalable wallets into your application\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\"},\"partners\":{\"tag\":\"Partners\",\"heading\":\"Building With Circle\",\"description\":\"Hackathon participants can integrate Circle's infrastructure and tools—including \u003cLinkCircleWallets\u003eCircle Wallets\u003c/LinkCircleWallets\u003e to build flexible, secure and scalable embedded wallets into applications, and \u003cLinkCCTP\u003eCCTP (Cross-Chain Transfer Protocol)\u003c/LinkCCTP\u003e to enable native USDC transfers between Aptos and other supported blockchains.\",\"ctaButton\":\"Explore Resources\"},\"resources\":{\"tag\":\"Tools \u0026 Docs\",\"heading\":\"Builder Resources\",\"description\":\"Access beginner guides, advanced tutorials, documentation, and workshops. Whether you're new to Move or expanding your expertise, you'll find the tools and support you need here.\",\"ctaButton\":\"Explore Resources\"},\"eventTimeline\":{\"tag\":\"Event Timeline\",\"heading\":\"Key dates to remember\"},\"bookEnd\":{\"tag\":\"Register\",\"heading\":\"Build the next big thing in DeFi. Build something that matters.\",\"description\":\"Connect, code, and collaborate on projects that will resonate across the universe.\",\"ctaButton\":\"Register Now\",\"secondaryButton\":\"View hackathon rules\"}},\"currentArticle\":{\"backButtonTitle\":\"Back to Currents\",\"backButtonLabel\":\"Back to All Articles\",\"newsletterFormTitle\":\"Get the Aptos newsletter delivered to your inbox\",\"newsletterFormSectionTitle\":\"Subscribe for Updates\"},\"currentArticlesIndex\":{\"tag\":\"Blog\",\"heroTitle\":\"Insights and Updates\",\"heroDescription\":\"Keep up with the latest across Aptos’ technical innovations, projects, and blockchain industry insights.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Aptos Blog: Insights and Updates\",\"metaDescription\":\"Keep up with the latest across Aptos’ technical innovations, projects, and blockchain industry insights.\",\"featured\":\"Featured\",\"readArticles\":\"Read Article\"},\"currentNotFound\":{\"description\":\"Blog post not found\",\"backButtonLabel\":\"Go to all blog posts\",\"backButtonTitle\":\"Back to all blog posts page\"},\"ecosystemJobs\":{\"metaTitle\":\"Web3 Jobs for a Decentralized Tomorrow - Aptos Ecosystem Jobs\",\"metaDescription\":\"Find a job in the Aptos ecosystem.\",\"tag\":\"Ecosystem Jobs\",\"heroTitle\":\"Web3 Jobs for a Decentralized Tomorrow\",\"client\":{\"searchForJob\":\"Search for a job\",\"jobFunction\":\"Job function\",\"noJobFunctions\":\"No job functions\",\"location\":\"Location\",\"noLocations\":\"No locations\",\"company\":\"Company\",\"noCompanies\":\"No companies\",\"createJobAlert\":\"Create job alert\",\"resetAll\":\"Reset all\",\"noJobsFound\":\"No jobs found. Try to change filters.\",\"alertDialog\":{\"title\":\"Be the first to know about new jobs\",\"description\":\"Get daily alerts when new jobs match your current filters\",\"submissionError\":\"Submission error. Please try again.\",\"formEmail\":\"Your Email\",\"formJobFunction\":\"Job Function\",\"formSubscribe\":\"Subscribe\",\"formSuccessMessage\":\"You are now subscribed to job alerts. You’ll receive a confirmation email shortly.\"}}},\"ecosystemProject\":{\"backToEcosystemProjects\":\"Ecosystem Projects\",\"otherCategory\":\"Other {category}\",\"viewAllCategory\":\"View All {category}\",\"platforms\":\"Platforms\",\"aboutProject\":\"About {projectName}\",\"readMore\":\"Read more\"},\"ecosystemProjectNotFound\":{\"description\":\"Project not found\",\"backButtonLabel\":\"Go to all ecosystem projects\",\"backButtonTitle\":\"Back to all ecosystem projects page\"},\"ecosystemProjects\":{\"client\":{\"metaSuffix\":\"Aptos Ecosystem Projects\",\"tag\":\"Ecosystem Projects\",\"heroTitleAllProjects\":\"Built on Aptos\",\"heroTitleCategoryProjects\":\"{category} on Aptos\",\"heroDescriptionAllProjects\":\"Discover projects within the Aptos Ecosystem.\",\"heroDescriptionCategoryProjects\":\"Discover {category} within the Aptos Ecosystem.\",\"all\":\"All\",\"filterProjectCategories\":\"Filter project categories\",\"showcaseYourProject\":\"Showcase Your Project\",\"openFilters\":\"Open filters\",\"resetAllFilters\":\"Reset all filters\",\"closeFilters\":\"Close filters\",\"close\":\"Close\",\"showOnlyGrantRecipients\":\"Show only grant recipients\",\"filterBy\":\"Filter by\",\"networks\":\"Networks\",\"features\":\"Features\",\"platforms\":\"Platforms\",\"allEcosystem\":\"All Ecosystem\",\"categoryProjectsOnAptos\":\"{categoryName} Projects on Aptos\",\"viewAllCategory\":\"View All {categoryName}\",\"searchInputLoadingPlaceholder\":\"Loading projects...\",\"searchInputPlaceholderAll\":\"{count, plural, =0 {No projects} other {Search # {count, plural, =1 {project} other {projects}}}}\",\"searchInputPlaceholder\":\"{count, plural, =0 {No {categoryName} projects} other {Search # {categoryName} {count, plural, =1 {project} other {projects}}}}\",\"noProjectsFound\":\"No projects found\",\"noProjectsFoundWithFilters\":\"No projects found. Try to change filters or \u003cresetButton\u003ereset\u003c/resetButton\u003e them.\",\"categoryNotFound\":\"The category you are looking for does not exist. \u003cresetButton\u003eShow all projects\u003c/resetButton\u003e.\"}},\"event\":{\"addToCalendar\":\"Add to Calendar\",\"addToGoogleCalendar\":\"Add to Google Calendar\",\"addToGoogleCalendarTitle\":\"Add to Google Calendar\",\"addToGoogleCalendarLabel\":\"Google Calendar\",\"addToMicrosoftOutlookTitle\":\"Add to Microsoft Outlook\",\"addToMicrosoftOutlookLabel\":\"Microsoft Outlook\",\"addToOffice365Title\":\"Add to Office 365\",\"addToOffice365Label\":\"Office 365\",\"addToYahooCalendarTitle\":\"Add to Yahoo Calendar\",\"addToYahooCalendarLabel\":\"Yahoo! Calendar\",\"addToICalTitle\":\"Add to iCal\",\"addToICalLabel\":\"iCal\",\"eventHasEnded\":\"This event has ended.\",\"date\":\"Date\",\"startDate\":\"Start\",\"endDate\":\"End\",\"virtualEvent\":\"Virtual Event\",\"shareTitle\":\"Share\",\"locationTitle\":\"Location\",\"eventOverview\":\"Event Overview\"},\"eventFlagship\":{\"sections\":{\"overview\":\"Overview\",\"speakers\":\"Speakers\",\"agendaDay1\":\"Agenda: Day 1\",\"agendaDay2\":\"Agenda: Day 2\",\"venue\":\"Venue\",\"officeHours\":\"Office Hours\",\"tickets\":\"Get Tickets\",\"faq\":\"Know Before You Go\"},\"metaTitle\":\"Aptos experience 2024\",\"mainLine\":\"Experience 24\",\"eventPlace\":\"Seoul, South Korea - September 5-6\",\"heroCta\":\"#ExperienceAptos\",\"description\":\"Join us for The Aptos Experience, an immersive journey into the heart and soul of Web3. We won’t just tell you about what the community is building—we’ll show you.\",\"moreToBeAnnounced\":\"…more to be announced\",\"agendaSubjectToChange\":\"Agenda tracks are subject to change.\",\"speakers\":{\"tag\":\"Speakers\",\"heading\":\"Featuring Tech Leaders \u0026 Web3 Innovators\"},\"overview\":{\"title\":\"Overview\",\"heading\":\"No passive participation allowed\",\"description\":\"Join us for The Aptos Experience, an immersive journey into the heart and soul of Web3. We won’t just tell you about what the community is building—we’ll show you.\",\"studioTitle\":\"Studio Time for Your Project\",\"studioDescription\":\"Engage in personalized 1:1 sessions and hands-on tutorials with leading developers.\",\"web3PioneersTitle\":\"Web3 Pioneers\",\"web3PioneersDescription\":\"Hear from industry leaders about the future of decentralization.\",\"networkingTitle\":\"Networking Opportunities\",\"networkingDescription\":\"Connect with fellow developers, entrepreneurs, and blockchain enthusiasts from around the world.\",\"announcementsTitle\":\"Exclusive Announcements\",\"announcementsDescription\":\"Be the first to hear about new features and upcoming projects within the Aptos ecosystem.\",\"seoulTitle\":\"The Best of Seoul\",\"seoulDescription\":\"Indulge in curated happy hours, dinners, and excursions each night, experiencing the best of what Seoul has to offer.\"},\"agendaDay1\":{\"title\":\"Agenda: Day 1\",\"description\":\"September 5, 2024\",\"item1Title\":\"Breakfast Bar\",\"item2Title\":\"Foundation Welcome Day 1\",\"item3Title\":\"The Aptos Vision: Building for Tomorrow, Together\",\"item4Title\":\"Energy, Compute \u0026 Crypto: Bringing Thermodynamics On-Chain\",\"item5Title\":\"Reimagining Payments: On-Chain Transactions with Mobile, Wallets, and Stablecoins\",\"item6Title\":\"Why Move Matters: Perspectives from an OG DeFi Investor and User\",\"item7Title\":\"Art, Sports, and Culture Meets Technology: Empowering Creativity \u0026 Digital Ownership\",\"item8Title\":\"Lunch\",\"item9Title\":\"High Performance Finance Meets Privacy on Aptos\",\"item10Title\":\"APACs Investment Potential \u0026 Key Drivers for Adoption\",\"item11Title\":\"Move It or Lose It: Powering Capital-Efficient Liquidity On-Chain\",\"item12Title\":\"NBC Universal's Web3 Journey\",\"item13Title\":\"Petra Announcement\",\"item14Title\":\"The DeFi Renaissance\",\"item15Title\":\"Web3 Gaming Revolution: New Innovations in Game Economics and Design\",\"item16Title\":\"Google on Aptos Gamestack\",\"item17Title\":\"The Future on Aptos: Deep Dive of Focus Areas for the Year Ahead\",\"item18Title\":\"Day 1 Wrap Up \u0026 Takeaways\",\"item19Title\":\"Networking \u0026 Drinks\",\"item20Title\":\"Night Shift (with Peaches)\"},\"agendaDay2\":{\"title\":\"Agenda: Day 2\",\"description\":\"September 6, 2024\",\"item1Title\":\"Breakfast Bar\",\"item2Title\":\"Foundation Welcome to Day 2\",\"item3Title\":\"Unlocking Your Creativity: Our Vision for Tech\",\"item4Title\":\"Asset Allocation in the Digital Age: Global Macro Trends and the Case for Crypto\",\"item5Title\":\"Bridging the Gap: Bringing Leading TradFi On-Chain with Aptos Ascend\",\"item6Title\":\"Build Omnichain on Aptos with LayerZero\",\"item7Title\":\"The Next Era of DeFi: Exploring What It Takes to Truly Scale\",\"item8Title\":\"How Web3 Is Transforming the Used Car Market\",\"item9Title\":\"Lunch\",\"item10Title\":\"Move 2: The Future of Move on Aptos is Here\",\"item11Title\":\"Builders Playbook: Technical Deep Dive on Leveraging Move for DeFi\",\"item12Title\":\"Digital Property Rights: The Great Value Unlock\",\"item13Title\":\"Onboarding the Masses: Strategies for Bringing Everyday Users On-Chain\",\"item14Title\":\"Our Experience: Building a Mutual Fund on Aptos\",\"item15Title\":\"Enterprise Adoption of Web3 in Korea: Use Cases and Benefits\",\"item16Title\":\"VC Perspectives: Navigating the Web3 Gaming Landscape\",\"item17Title\":\"Crypto's Next Chapter: The Hybridization of DeFi and CeFi Markets\",\"item18Title\":\"Mo + Meltem\",\"item19Title\":\"Closing Remarks\",\"item20Title\":\"Aptos Afters\"},\"officeHours\":{\"title\":\"Office Hours\",\"heading\":\"Looking for expert guidance on building or scaling your dApps?\",\"description\":\"During The Aptos Experience, we’re offering on-site Office Hours to provide you with personalized, 1:1 technical support. Whether you’re seeking advice on development strategies, troubleshooting, or scaling your next big idea, this is your opportunity to connect directly with leading engineers.\",\"updateDescription\":\"UPDATE: All scheduled slots have been filled, but you can still register in person during the event. Be sure to ask at the front desk when you check in.\"},\"venue\":{\"tag\":\"Venue\",\"title\":\"Connecting minds at XYZ Seoul\",\"description\":\"Experience the vibrant atmosphere of XYZ Seoul, the largest cultural complex on Yeonmujang-gil, as we host our special event. Immerse yourself in a celebration of innovation and community, set in this unique cultural destination.\",\"bigPictureAlt\":\"XYZ Seoul exterior\",\"smallPicture1Alt\":\"XYZ Seoul interior\",\"smallPicture2Alt\":\"XYZ Seoul balcony\"},\"tickets\":{\"title\":\"Tickets\",\"description\":\"Aptos Experience is SOLD OUT\",\"overview\":\"General Admission Passes for The Aptos Experience are sold out online. We’ve reserved a limited number of last-minute “walk-up” tickets for builders attending KBW who would like to register in person.\",\"ticketType\":\"General Admission [SOLD OUT]\",\"getTickets\":\"Get your ticket\"},\"addEventToCalendarDialog\":{\"title\":\"Add Event to Calendar\"},\"confirmationDialog\":{\"title\":\"Registration Confirmed\",\"contentTitle\":\"Thank you for joining The Aptos Experience!\",\"contentParagraph1\":\"Check your inbox for your event confirmation and ticket receipt. Your confirmation email might have been routed to your spam folder, so be sure to check that as well. If you experience issues, reach out to \u003clink\u003eevents@aptosfoundation.org\u003c/link\u003e.\",\"contentParagraph2\":\"As we get closer to The Aptos Experience, we’ll follow up with more details and things to know before you go. Until then, we look forward to seeing you in September!\"},\"faq\":{\"tag\":\"FAQ\",\"title\":\"Know Before You Go\",\"item1Title\":\"Venue Information\",\"item1Content\":\"\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003eThe main event will take place at XYZ Seoul. Navigating the venue is designed to be straightforward and user-friendly. If you need assistance at any point, on-site guides will be stationed throughout, ready to help with directions, answer any questions, or provide additional information.\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\",\"item2Title\":\"Airport Information\",\"item2Content\":\"\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003eIncheon International Airport (ICN) is located approximately 60 kilometers (38 miles) away from the city. Depending on traffic conditions, the commute from ICN to Seoul typically takes between 1 to 1.5 hours.\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003eTaxis are easily accessible—once you exit the Passenger Terminal follow the signs to the taxi stand. There are usually staff at the stand who can direct you to the appropriate taxi for your destination.\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\",\"item3Title\":\"Travel Documentation\",\"item3Content\":\"\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003eWhile it may not be strictly required at this time, we recommend that you complete the \u003cLink\u003eKorea Travel Form\u003c/Link\u003e in advance for your convenience. This form may simplify your entry process into South Korea and remains valid for up to 2 years.\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\",\"item4Title\":\"Getting Around Seoul\",\"item4Content\":\"\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cHeading\u003eTaxis\u003c/Heading\u003e Readily available throughout the city.\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cHeading\u003eUber\u003c/Heading\u003e Operates in the area for your convenience.\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cHeading\u003ePublic Transit\u003c/Heading\u003e Efficient and well-connected. Consistently voted as one of the best in the world for its ease of use, cleanliness, and frequency of service, the Seoul subway system is one of the most efficient ways to travel around the city. \u003cLink\u003eLearn more about public transportation options.\u003c/Link\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cHeading\u003eNavigation\u003c/Heading\u003e For directions and accurate location of destinations in Seoul, we recommend using the KakaoMap App. Google Maps and Apple Maps may not always be reliable in the area.\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\",\"item5Title\":\"Things to do nearby (local attractions \u0026 places to shop)\",\"item5Content\":\"$1f\"}},\"eventNotFound\":{\"description\":\"Event not Found\",\"backButtonLabel\":\"Go to all events\",\"backButtonTitle\":\"Back to all events page\"},\"eventsIndex\":{\"tag\":\"Events\",\"heroTitle\":\"Decentralized gatherings around the globe\",\"heroDescription\":\"Experience the future of blockchain at our global event series, where innovators and industry leaders from around the world converge to shape tomorrow.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Global Gatherings: Join Our Premier Blockchain Events Worldwide\",\"metaDescription\":\"Experience the future of blockchain at our global event series, where innovators and industry leaders from around the world converge to shape tomorrow.\",\"audience\":\"Aptos Developers\",\"featured\":\"Featured\",\"upcomingEvents\":\"Upcoming Events\",\"getEventDetails\":\"Get event details\",\"pastEvents\":\"Past Events\"},\"getStarted\":{\"metaTitle\":\"Get Started on Aptos\",\"metaDescription\":\"From giant enterprises to teams of one, Aptos is the next generation L1 blockchain where anyone can build the future of Web3.\",\"sections\":{\"network\":\"Network\",\"foundation\":\"Foundation\",\"governance\":\"Governance\",\"moveLang\":\"Move Language\",\"moveModules\":\"Move Modules\",\"grants\":\"Grants\",\"ecosystem\":\"Ecosystem\",\"web3wallets\":\"Web3 Wallets\",\"blockExplorers\":\"Block Explorers\",\"nfts\":\"NFTs\",\"web3gaming\":\"Web3 Gaming\",\"defi\":\"DeFi\"},\"networkTitle\":\"Aptos Network\",\"networkDescription\":\"Aptos is a Layer-1 community-driven network, governed by the people who build on it from around the world. It’s decentralized. It’s fast. It’s blockchain at its best.\",\"networkDescription2\":\"Build community, make change, do something different. No need to ask for access. This blockchain is permissionless. Just build.\",\"networkReadWhitepaper\":\"Read the Aptos Whitepaper\",\"foundationTitle\":\"What’s the Aptos Foundation?\",\"foundationDescription\":\"The Aptos Foundation is like the Aptos blockchain’s steadfast teammate–supporting its endeavors, bolstering it during challenges, and celebrating its triumphs.\",\"foundationDescription2\":\" Dedicated to cultivating the ecosystem, it empowers teams and individuals with grants, invigorates community engagement through educational programs and events, and champions decentralization via partnerships with node validators.\",\"governanceTitle\":\"Governance\",\"governanceDescription\":\"The power to the future of Aptos is in your hands. If you’re a part of the Aptos community, you can propose improvements or new ideas and vote on Aptos Improvement Proposals (AIPs for short).\",\"governanceDescription2\":\"Help guide the future of the network–from framework upgrades to changes to core code. Influence. Vote.\",\"governanceVote\":\"Vote\",\"governanceReadMore\":\"More Resources\",\"moveLangTitle\":\"Move Language\",\"moveLangDescription\":\"The Move Language is the backbone of the Aptos network. Move introduces a safer, faster, and more expressive way to craft decentralized applications (aka Dapps).\",\"moveLangDescription2\":\"Devs love it. It’s effortless, like “chewing cotton candy.”\",\"moveLangMaster\":\"Master Move\",\"moveModulesTitle\":\"Move Modules\",\"moveModulesDescription\":\"Some call them smart contracts. But, on Aptos, they’re called Move modules. The important thing is, they can’t be changed, tampered, altered, or messed with in any way.\",\"moveModulesDescription2\":\"Start writing your first Move module on Aptos.\",\"moveModulesStartCoding\":\"Start Coding\",\"grantsTitle\":\"Grants\",\"grantsDescription\":\"You and your ideas make the Aptos community thrive. Find the right launch pad to help your projects take flight.\",\"grantsDescription2\":\"Whether you’re an individual developer or a team, you can apply for a grant and get the funding you need to bring your ideas to life.\",\"grantsApplyForGrant\":\"Apply for a Grant\",\"ecosystemTitle\":\"Aptos Ecosystem\",\"ecosystemDescription\":\"Your ideas are at the center of the Aptos ecosystem. Developers, creators, and users all come together to push the boundaries of what’s possible with blockchain.\",\"ecosystemDescription2\":\"Get a sneak peek into the various projects built in the Aptos Ecosystem and how you can get started with your own.\",\"ecosystemExploreProjects\":\"Explore Projects\",\"ecosystemBuildDApp\":\"Build a Dapp\",\"web3walletsTitle\":\"Web3 Wallets\",\"web3walletsDescription\":\"Take control of your privacy and manage all your assets on Aptos. Aptos wallets provide a secure and efficient way to track all your digital assets.\",\"web3walletsDescription2\":\"Learn about the standards we’ve set for our wallets and how they can enhance your experience on Aptos.\",\"web3walletsGuidelines\":\"See Wallet Guidelines\",\"web3walletsAdapter\":\"Wallet Adapter\",\"web3walletsEcosystem\":\"Ecosystem Wallets\",\"blockExplorersTitle\":\"Block Explorers\",\"blockExplorersDescription\":\"Explore the block and see transactions happening on Aptos.\",\"blockExplorersDescription2\":\"It’s how you’ll understand the health of the network, and how the blockchain stays transparent.\",\"blockExplorersScanAptos\":\"Scan Aptos\",\"nftsTitle\":\"NFTs\",\"nftsDescription\":\"NFTs aren’t just for creators and collectors, they’re for everyone. It’s just a techie term for saying, “it’s unique, and it’s yours.”\",\"nftsDescription2\":\"Explore the world of NFTs on Aptos, learn how to mint your first one, and see how you can own a piece of NFT culture.\",\"nftsCreateNFT\":\"Create an NFT\",\"nftsNavigateTools\":\"Navigate NFT Tools\",\"moreResources\":\"More Resources\",\"web3gamingTitle\":\"Web3 Gaming\",\"web3gamingDescription\":\"Aptos lets you own and take your achievements outside the game and into the Web3 world.\",\"web3gamingDescription2\":\"Check out what gamers are building on Aptos and how they’re redefining asset ownership.\",\"web3gamingExploreProjects\":\"Explore Gaming Projects\",\"defiTitle\":\"Decentralized Finance (DeFi)\",\"defiDescription\":\"DeFi is pushing the boundaries of modern-day banking and value transfer.\",\"defiDescription2\":\"Decentralized Financial applications built on Aptos bring simple and complex monetary transactions alike to a level playing field for all users.\",\"defiDiveInto\":\"Dive into DeFi\"},\"grant\":{\"newLabel\":\"New\",\"overview\":\"Overview\",\"guidingPrinciples\":\"Guiding Principles\",\"acceptingApplications\":\"Now Accepting Applications\",\"applicationsPaused\":\"Applications Paused\",\"ourPartnersPrograms\":\"Programs by our Partners\",\"apply\":\"Apply\",\"faq\":\"FAQ\",\"otherGrants\":\"Other Grants\"},\"grantNotFound\":{\"description\":\"Grant not found\",\"backButtonLabel\":\"Go to all grants\",\"backButtonTitle\":\"Back to all grants page\"},\"grantsIndex\":{\"tag\":\"Grants\",\"intro\":\"We invite builders to apply for grants to enhance community engagement, foster educational initiatives, and champion the cause of Aptos and decentralization.\",\"recipientsTitle\":\"Grant Recipients\",\"recipientsDescription\":\"200+ Grant Recipients …and counting\",\"recipientsViewAll\":\"View More Recipients\",\"storiesTitle\":\"Grant Impact Stories\",\"storiesDescription\":\"From vision to Mainnet \u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e Grant recipients share their real-world stories\",\"currentProgramsTitle\":\"Current Programs\",\"currentProgramsDescription\":\"Choose a program and apply today\",\"guidingPrinciplesTitle\":\"Guiding Principles\",\"guidingPrinciplesDescription\":\"Guiding principles for grant applications\",\"ourPartnersProgramsTitle\":\"Partner Programs\",\"ourPartnersProgramsDescription\":\"Explore opportunities from external partners\",\"faqTitle\":\"FAQ\",\"faqDescription\":\"Common questions about the application process\"},\"lfm\":{\"metaTitle\":\"Aptos LFM - The Premier TGE Track for Aptos Projects\",\"metaDescription\":\"LFM supports market-tested projects gearing up for TGE with hands-on support, ecosystem connections, and growth strategy to become ecosystem leaders.\",\"heroCta\":\"Join the Collective\",\"tag\":\"Aptos Collective\",\"heroTitle\":\"Join a community that shares your passion!\",\"intro\":\"Beyond membership perks and the chance to champion a community you're passionate about—the Collective is also a movement. We’re building the future of Aptos.\",\"programStructure\":{\"tag\":\"Program Structure\",\"title\":\"Your own dedicated growth engine\",\"card1Title\":\"Intensive Kick-off Workshop\",\"card1Description\":\"LFM kicks off with a weeklong in-person workshop with ecosystem leaders, focused on strategic planning to tailor program requirements and support.\",\"card2Title\":\"Personalized Growth Squad\",\"card2Description\":\"Participants are supported by a dedicated program lead and team, with direct access to experts in engineering, marketing, and strategy from Aptos Foundation \u0026 Aptos Labs.\",\"card3Title\":\"Expert Mentorship \u0026 Access\",\"card3Description\":\"An elite network of external industry leaders, mentors, and investors await. Get strategic guidance during 1:1 sessions and office hours.\",\"card4Title\":\"Exclusive Networking \u0026 Events\",\"card4Description\":\"Private networking events connect participants with investors and program partners. Take part in exclusive workshops and roundtables with ecosystem leaders for deeper collaboration.\",\"card5Title\":\"Tailored Resources \u0026 Tools\",\"card5Description\":\"A members-only resource library provides templates and guides, along with access to premium tools and promotional resources to support growth.\"},\"supportAreas\":{\"tag\":\"Support Areas\",\"title\":\"Multidisciplinary support to fuel TGE readiness\",\"description\":\"Comprehensive support across key areas to ensure your project's success.\",\"card1Title\":\"Legal\",\"card1Description\":\"Explore considerations regarding legal \u0026 regulatory topics through office hours with experts.\",\"card2Title\":\"Fundraising Readiness\",\"card2Description\":\"Refine your pitch deck and prepare for investor demos with coaching from top advisors on pitching techniques.\",\"card3Title\":\"Tokenomics\",\"card3Description\":\"Learn about token model optimization, including token distribution, airdrop structuring, vesting strategy, utility \u0026 long-term sustainability.\",\"card4Title\":\"Security Assessments\",\"card4Description\":\"Learn about security best practices with checklists \u0026 risk feedback, gain access to top-tier auditors \u0026 security experts, and explore security audit grants up to $25,000 for qualifying projects.\",\"card5Title\":\"Marketing Support\",\"card5Description\":\"Leverage social amplification \u0026 content marketing support, learn community growth strategies \u0026 best practices, and access grants available to support marketing campaigns.\",\"card6Title\":\"Listings\",\"card6Description\":\"Learn best practices for DEX and CEX engagement with introductions to top-tier exchanges \u0026 pitching support.\"},\"faq\":{\"tag\":\"Faq\",\"title\":\"Common questions about LFM\",\"item1Title\":\"What makes LFM different?\",\"item1Content\":\"Unlike traditional incubators or accelerators, LFM focuses on post-launch projects with demonstrated on-chain traction. Our goal is to provide multidisciplinary support—from security to marketing and beyond—to help projects successfully navigate their TGE journey. With expert guidance, a dedicated support team, and access to a powerful network, LFM positions teams for sustainable growth and long-term impact.\",\"item2Title\":\"Who can apply?\",\"item2Content\":\"LFM is designed for strong Aptos-native projects that are approaching a Token Generation Event. We assess eligibility based on demonstrated on-chain traction, team capability, and potential ecosystem impact.\\n\\nIf you're still pre-launch, check out our \u003cLinkGrants\u003eGrants\u003c/LinkGrants\u003e for other avenues of support.\",\"item3Title\":\"What kind of support can I expect?\",\"item3Content\":\"We provide tailored, hands-on support based on your project’s TGE readiness. Our network of domain-specific experts covers community building, exchange listings, fundraising, legal, security, and more—ensuring you get the right resources for your TGE journey.\",\"item4Title\":\"Does LFM provide funding?\",\"item4Content\":\"LFM participants have access to a dedicated grant pool that can be deployed for various growth initiatives including marketing campaigns, security audits, community building, and other types of support. Additionally, select projects may be considered for strategic investment. Grant allocations are determined based on project needs and alignment with program objectives.\",\"item5Title\":\"Are there any fees or terms if I am accepted into the program?\",\"item5Content\":\"No, the program is free.\",\"item6Title\":\"Do you provide learning resources for projects?\",\"item6Content\":\"Yes! We offer a content library with playbooks, templates, and strategic guides, plus webinars, workshops, and investor insights to help projects stay ahead.\",\"item7Title\":\"How long does the program last?\",\"item7Content\":\"Instead of a fixed-duration program, LFM offers modular support that adapts and evolves with your project’s growth trajectory. Each team receives a customized program with targeted resources, tools, and expert guidance delivered exactly when needed.\",\"item8Title\":\"What is the selection criteria for LFM?\",\"item8Content\":\"LFM is designed for Aptos-native projects with proven, early traction \u0026 high-growth potential. We assess program eligibility based on:\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003eOn-chain activity \u0026 community engagement\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003eTeam strength \u0026 execution capability\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003eProject potential \u0026 ecosystem impact\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003eFunding status\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003eNot quite there yet? We have other resources to help you grow!\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cList\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cLinkGrants\u003eApply for grants →\u003c/LinkGrants\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cLinkDocs\u003eView developer docs →\u003c/LinkDocs\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003cListItem\u003e\u003cLinkCommunity\u003eExplore the community →\u003c/LinkCommunity\u003e\u003c/ListItem\u003e\u003c/List\u003e\",\"item9Title\":\"How do I apply to LFM?\",\"item9Content\":\"\u003cLinkSubmitApplication\u003eSubmit a short application\u003c/LinkSubmitApplication\u003e with key project details; applications are reviewed on a rolling basis.\",\"item10Title\":\"How long is the selection process?\",\"item10Content\":\"Applications will be evaluated on a rolling basis, and we aim respond within one week.\"},\"apply\":{\"tag\":\"Apply\",\"title\":\"Join the next wave of high-impact Web3 projects on Aptos.\",\"description\":\"We review applications on a rolling basis—and new members are welcomed every month. To optimize your chances, we recommend applicants familiarize themselves with the community by being a regular member of it for a few months prior.\",\"ctaButton\":\"Apply Now\"}},\"main\":{\"heroTitle\":\"MAKE YOUR MOVE\",\"aboutAptosTitle\":\"About Aptos\",\"aboutAptos\":\"Aptos is the blockchain network with everything you need to \u003chighlighted\u003ebuild your big idea.\u003c/highlighted\u003e Let’s Move.\",\"aptosInActionTitle\":\"Aptos in Action\",\"aptosInAction\":\"Your big idea meets its match. \u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003chighlighted\u003eBring it to life\u003c/highlighted\u003e on Aptos.\",\"useCasesTitle\":\"Use Cases\",\"useCasesViewAll\":\"View All Use Cases\",\"useCaseReadOne\":\"Read Use Case\",\"ourCommunityTitle\":\"Our Community\",\"ourCommunity\":\"Building connections with\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003chighlighted\u003eour dedicated community.\u003c/highlighted\u003e\",\"eventsTitle\":\"Upcoming Event\",\"eventsViewAll\":\"View All Events\",\"eventsCoverAlt\":\"Cover of {eventTitle} event\",\"eventsReadOne\":\"Get event details\",\"connectTitle\":\"Connect with Aptos\",\"connectTalkTitle\":\"Talk\",\"connectTalk\":\"Join the Forum to gather, share, and collab on all things Aptos.\",\"connectExploreTitle\":\"Explore\",\"connectExplore\":\"Discover live projects in the Aptos ecosystem.\",\"connectCurrentsTitle\":\"Stay Current\",\"connectCurrents\":\"Check the Blog and keep up with the latest news across the Aptos Network.\",\"networkNumbersTPS\":\"All-Time Peak TPS\",\"networkNumbersMAU\":\"All-Time Peak MAU\",\"networkNumbersTransactions\":\"Transactions\",\"networkNumbersTotalNodes\":\"Total Nodes\",\"networkNumbersValidatorNodes\":\"Validator Nodes\",\"networkNumbersTitle\":\"Aptos by the numbers*\",\"networkNumbers\":\"Revolutionizing \u003chighlighted\u003eBlockchain\u003c/highlighted\u003e\",\"networkNumbersDescription\":\"Unrivaled Speed, Unprecedented Trust, and an Unstoppable Community.\",\"networkNumbersFootnote\":\"*Data from internal indexing of on-chain activity on Aptos mainnet as of {updatedAt,date,long}\",\"pressTitle\":\"Press\",\"press\":\"People Are Talking\",\"globeImageText\":\"People Entertainment Defi NFTs Social Scalability Gaming\"},\"notFound\":{\"description\":\"Page Not Found\",\"backButtonLabel\":\"Go to main page\",\"backButtonTitle\":\"Back to main page\"},\"subscribe\":{\"metaTitle\":\"Newsletter subscription\",\"metaDescription\":\"Subscribe to our newsletter to get the latest news and updates.\",\"title\":\"Subscribe for Updates\",\"description\":\"Periodically receive network news, helpful resources, upcoming events and other offers you might be interested in.\"},\"useCase\":{\"backToUseCasesTitle\":\"Back to Use Cases\"},\"useCaseNotFound\":{\"description\":\"Use case not found\",\"backButtonLabel\":\"Go to all use cases\",\"backButtonTitle\":\"Back to all use cases page\"},\"useCasesIndex\":{\"tag\":\"Use Cases\",\"metaTitle\":\"Use Cases\",\"metaDescription\":\"Real-world deployments of our blockchain technology\",\"heroTitle\":\"Real-world deployments\",\"heroDescription\":\"Discover how organizations around the world are utilizing the Aptos blockchain to address complex challenges and create innovative solutions.\",\"featuredUseCases\":\"Featured Use Case\",\"readUseCase\":\"Read Use Case\"},\"whitepaper\":{\"metaTitle\":\"Aptos Whitepaper: Safe, Scalable, and Upgradeable Web3 Infrastructure\",\"metaDescription\":\"An introductory paper to Aptos, outlining a more accessible and efficient blockchain ecosystem designed for unparalleled accessibility and efficiency.\",\"whitepaperName\":\"Aptos Whitepaper\",\"whitepaperNameTranslation\":\"Aptos Whitepaper ({language})\",\"readFullWhitepaper\":\"Read the Full Whitepaper\",\"readFullAptosWhitepaper\":\"Read the full Aptos Whitepaper\",\"whitepaperOriginal\":\"Original version\",\"whitepaperKorean\":\"Korean translation\",\"whitepaperJapanese\":\"Japanese translation\",\"whitepaperEspanol\":\"Spanish translation\",\"tag\":\"Aptos Whitepaper\",\"heroTitle\":\"Safe, Scalable, and Upgradeable Web3 Infrastructure\",\"description\":\"The rise of blockchains as a new Internet infrastructure has led to developers deploying tens of thousands of decentralized applications at rapidly growing rates.\",\"paragraph1\":\"Unfortunately, blockchain usage is not yet ubiquitous due to frequent outages, high costs, low throughput limits, and numerous security concerns. To enable mass adoption in the web3 era, blockchain infrastructure needs to follow the path of cloud infrastructure as a trusted, scalable, cost-efficient, and continually improving platform for building widely-used applications.\",\"paragraph2\":\"We present the Aptos blockchain, designed with scalability, safety, reliability, and upgradeability as key principles, to address these challenges. The Aptos blockchain has been developed over the past three years by over 350+ developers across the globe. It offers new and novel innovations in consensus, smart contract design, system security, performance, and decentralization. The combination of these technologies will provide a fundamental building block to bring web3 to the masses:\",\"advantagesList1\":\"First, the Aptos blockchain natively integrates and internally uses the Move language for fast and secure transaction execution. The Move prover, a formal verifier for smart contracts written in the Move language, provides additional safeguards for contract invariants and behavior. This focus on security allows developers to better protect their software from malicious entities.\",\"advantagesList2\":\"Second, the Aptos data model enables flexible key management and hybrid custodial options. This, alongside transaction transparency prior to signing and practical light client protocols, provides a safer and more trustworthy user experience.\",\"advantagesList3\":\"Third, to achieve high throughput and low latency, the Aptos blockchain leverages a pipelined and modular approach for the key stages of transaction processing. Specifically, transaction dissemination, block metadata ordering, parallel transaction execution, batch storage, and ledger certification all operate concurrently. This approach fully leverages all available physical resources, improves hardware efficiency, and enables highly parallel execution.\",\"advantagesList4\":\"Fourth, unlike other parallel execution engines that break transaction atomicity by requiring upfront knowledge of the data to be read and written, the Aptos blockchain does not put such limitations on developers. It can efficiently support atomicity with arbitrarily complex transactions, enabling higher throughput and lower latency for real-world applications and simplifying development.\",\"advantagesList5\":\"Fifth, the Aptos modular architecture design supports client flexibility and optimizes for frequent and instant upgrades. Moreover, to rapidly deploy new technology innovations and support new web3 use cases, the Aptos blockchain provides embedded on-chain change management protocols.\",\"advantagesList6\":\"Finally, the Aptos blockchain is experimenting with future initiatives to scale beyond individual validator performance: its modular design and parallel execution engine support internal sharding of a validator and homogeneous state sharding provides the potential for horizontal throughput scalability without adding additional complexity for node operators.\",\"allTranslationsList\":\"Full Aptos Whitepaper\"}},\"terms\":{\"aptos\":\"Aptos\",\"github\":\"Github\",\"discord\":\"Discord\",\"twitter\":\"Twitter\"},\"toolbox\":{\"docs\":\"Docs\",\"explorer\":\"Explorer\",\"forum\":\"Forum\",\"names\":\"Aptos Names\"}},\"now\":\"$undefined\",\"timeZone\":\"UTC\",\"children\":\"$L20\"}]\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"21:I[42577,[\"4754\",\"static/chunks/4754-8aab191705aa8914.js\",\"8710\",\"static/chunks/8710-cc4bbfe7e72eb54f.js\",\"7934\",\"static/chunks/7934-0cec3d18aac18c43.js\",\"3306\",\"static/chunks/3306-908f080a9a1cc778.js\",\"389\",\"static/chunks/389-51c1b87db90f8dae.js\",\"6810\",\"static/chunks/6810-a37043eec9a35475.js\",\"193\",\"static/chunks/193-775e1679e7919a77.js\",\"1530\",\"static/chunks/1530-ba2e908260754a27.js\",\"736\",\"static/chunks/736-90fbeabe1eb32966.js\",\"9712\",\"static/chunks/9712-3a281a0aefbad4a8.js\",\"9662\",\"static/chunks/9662-a9aa1fbb00165833.js\",\"8450\",\"static/chunks/app/%5Blocale%5D/layout-0c8176871ea03a8a.js\"],\"PageOnLoad\"]\n22:I[31340,[\"4754\",\"static/chunks/4754-8aab191705aa8914.js\",\"8710\",\"static/chunks/8710-cc4bbfe7e72eb54f.js\",\"7934\",\"static/chunks/7934-0cec3d18aac18c43.js\",\"3306\",\"static/chunks/3306-908f080a9a1cc778.js\",\"389\",\"static/chunks/389-51c1b87db90f8dae.js\",\"6810\",\"static/chunks/6810-a37043eec9a35475.js\",\"193\",\"static/chunks/193-775e1679e7919a77.js\",\"1530\",\"static/chunks/1530-ba2e908260754a27.js\",\"736\",\"static/chunks/736-90fbeabe1eb32966.js\",\"9712\",\"static/chunks/9712-3a281a0aefbad4a8.js\",\"9662\",\"static/chunks/9662-a9aa1fbb00165833.js\",\"8450\",\"static/chunks/app/%5Blocale%5D/layout-0c8176871ea03a8a.js\"],\"SkipToContent\"]\n"])</script><script>self._